Name: pymycity
Version: 0.2.6
Summary: Get your city live information
Home-page: http://github.com/titilambert/pymycity
Author: Thibault Cohen
Author-email: titilambert@gmail.com
License: UNKNOWN
Description: ########
        PyMyCity
        ########
        
        Supported cities
        ################
        
        * Mascouche: https://ville.mascouche.qc.ca
        * Montréal: http://ville.montreal.qc.ca
        
        Installation
        ############
        
        ::
        
            pip install pymycity
        
        
        Usage
        #####
        
        ::
        
            ± pymycity 
            usage: pymycity [-h] [-T TIMEOUT] {mascouche,montreal} ...
        
        
            Cities:
                * mascouche:
                    + garbage_collection:
                        - List next garbage collection
                    + taxes:
                        - List next taxes dates
                    + events:
                        - List next city events
                * montreal:
                    + taxes:
                        - List next taxes dates
        
        Dev env
        #######
        
        ::
        
            virtualenv -p /usr/bin/python3 env
            pip install -r requirements.txt
        
